{"tid":724556,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港大數據】林鄭「粉絲」：老人、低學歷者、主婦","createTime":"2018-07-01T04:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T23:59:26.000Z","uid":53379,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6d20b52b9a544bab337e231fb154dcf8273b37d1","tid":724556,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T04:19:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【港大數據】林鄭「粉絲」：老人、低學歷者、主婦</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n眾新聞向香港大學民意研究計劃，索取過去一年特首支持度調查的原始數據，再按年齡、教育水平、職業等人口特徵作分析，剖析社會不同群組對特首林鄭月娥的支持度差異。<br />\n<br />\n老、中、青三代香港人，對林鄭的支持程度相去多遠？<br />\n<br />\n中學年年考第一的「高材生」林鄭，做特首會否獲高學歷市民評高分？<br />\n<br />\n在行政及專業人士、學生、家庭主婦群組內，林鄭的支持者佔多，抑或反對者佔多？<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞分析發現，老人、低學歷者、主婦群組有大量的林鄭「粉絲」；青年、高學歷者、學生，則是相對最少林鄭支持者的群組。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2017/01/%E8%A1%8C%E4%B9%9E-%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E6%88%B0-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-20170128014347_11de_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2017%2F01%2F%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25B9%259E-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5-20170128014347_11de_large.jpg&h=e87923ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭參選特首期間，落區時曾遇到一名行乞內地老婦，林鄭當時給予對方一張500元鈔票，有輿論指她「離地」。眾新聞分析發現，老人、低學歷、主婦，都是林鄭獲大比數支持的群組。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港大學民意研究計劃每月進行兩次特首民調，邀請受訪者為特首評分，0分代表「絕對唔支持」，100分代表「絕對支持」，50分則代表「一半半」。<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞將林鄭月娥上任特首以來，自去年7月初至今年6月中的24次評分數據，按年齡、職業、教育水平群組分類，再將各群組對林鄭的評分分布製作成以下的氣泡圖（bubble chart）： 0分至100分由左至右排列，氣泡位置高低代表評林鄭相關分數的受訪者比率平均值，氣泡面積大小則反映評分人數多少。換言之，氣泡愈高、愈大，則代表該群組內愈多人向林鄭評予相關分數。<br />\n<br />\n比年齡：青年 VS 中年 VS 老年<br />\n綜觀青年（18至29歲）、中年（50至59歲）、老年（70歲或以上）群組的氣泡分布，可見各群組對林鄭的態度有明顯差異。<br />\n<br />\n評予林鄭50分的受訪者比率，在各群組均屬最高，約佔各群組整體受訪人數的兩成，青年、中年、老年群組分別有22.8%、19.5%、17.3%。三個群組的氣泡圖上，中央位置最高、最大的氣泡，便代表這群對林鄭態度「一半半」的受訪者。<br />\n<br />\n50分氣泡的左邊，代表評予林鄭50分以下、傾向不支持她的受訪者；而50分氣泡的右邊，代表評予林鄭50分以上、傾向支持她的受訪者。隨受訪者年齡增加，較大的氣泡傾向集中於右邊，顯示評高分的受訪者比率較高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/06/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-20180630001110_2271_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F06%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5-20180630001110_2271_large.png&h=9e8d52ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在青年群組的氣泡圖上，左邊有較多較大的氣泡，反映傾向不支持林鄭的受訪者佔多。而在中年及老年群組的氣泡圖上，較大的氣泡則集中在右邊，反映傾向支持林鄭的受訪者佔多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/06/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-20180630001046_2837_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F06%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-20180630001046_2837_large.png&h=69cc4189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/06/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-20180630001100_68bc_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F06%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5-20180630001100_68bc_large.png&h=072aa1d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老年群組中，大多數受訪者都非常支持林鄭，評100分的比率逾一成（12.5%），向林鄭評予60分、70分、80分、90分、100分的受訪者共佔56.3%；評0分、10分、20分、30分、40分的合共僅佔8.8%。但在青年群組中，單計評0分的受訪者已接近一成（9.6%）。<br />\n<br />\n比學歷：小學 VS 中學 VS 大學<br />\n學歷群組與年齡群組的評分走勢相反。隨受訪者學歷遞增，右邊的氣泡傾向縮小、左邊的氣泡傾向擴大，顯示評高分的受訪者比率減少、評低分的比率增加。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/06/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-20180630001757_793d_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F06%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-20180630001757_793d_large.png&h=b302ef94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/06/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96-20180630001737_f07a_large.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F06%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596-20180630001737_f07a_large.png&d=RlaUV3mby5HUmnw0THZF02xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=41aadb0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/06/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96-20180630001737_f07a_large.png</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n小學或以下學歷群組中，逾半數受訪者向林鄭評予50分以上，超過兩成給50分，僅不足一成評50分以下。中學學歷群組，仍是評高分的居多，但評50分以上的比率已見減少。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/06/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-20180630001749_297e_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F06%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5-20180630001749_297e_large.png&h=f90575c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在大學或以上學歷群組，評50分以上及50分以下的比率進一步拉近，向林鄭評予60分、70分、80分、90分、100分的受訪者共佔37.5%，而評0分、10分、20分、30分、40分的受訪者共佔28%。 <br />\n<br />\n比職業：行政及專業人士 VS 學生 VS 家庭主婦<br />\n在行政及專業人士、學生、家庭主婦群組，評予林鄭50分的受訪者比率都是最高，佔群組整體約兩成。家庭主婦及學生對林鄭支持度的差異最大。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/06/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-20180630002037_2531_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F06%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5-20180630002037_2531_large.png&h=cf5a1cf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 學生群組的氣泡分布較為平均， 代表評予林鄭50分以上、50分以下的比率參半。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/06/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-20180630002046_1d14_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F06%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594-20180630002046_1d14_large.png&h=95aaa4ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在家庭主婦群組中，受訪者對林鄭的態度可謂大比數支持，評100分的比率逾一成（12.1%），向林鄭評予60分、70分、80分、90分、100分的受訪者共佔高達62.5%；評0分、10分、20分、30分、40分的合共佔15.8%。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/06/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-20180630002029_1742_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F06%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594-20180630002029_1742_large.png&h=78c2261e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政及專業人士群組的氣泡分布，與家庭主婦群組的相似，較大的氣泡集中在右邊，顯示給林鄭評高分者居多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/13101/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85-13101/%E3%80%90%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E3%80%91%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E3%80%8C%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9A%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%81%E4%BD%8E%E5%AD%B8%E6%AD%B7%E8%80%85%E3%80%81%E4%B8%BB%E5%A9%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F13101%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585-13101%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25B2%2589%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E3%2580%258D%25EF%25BC%259A%25E8%2580%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E3%2580%2581%25E4%25BD%258E%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E3%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25A9%25A6&d=RlaUV3mby5HUmnw0THZF02xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=0d753596\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/13101/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85-13101/%E3%80%90%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E3%80%91%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E3%80%8C%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9A%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%81%E4%BD%8E%E5%AD%B8%E6%AD%B7%E8%80%85%E3%80%81%E4%B8%BB%E5%A9%A6</a>"},{"pid":"15e6dd1bc168a87ce4da59924f7b13bd5945dd7c","tid":724556,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T04:21:44.000Z","msg":"少左訓移民，綜援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e78cd97850e98be884545a92a8dc858ae271f6","tid":724556,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T04:22:31.000Z","msg":"越窮越撐地產霸權代理人 咁矛盾"},{"pid":"e91a2d0e206839e40127abfbdd6c82f428142830","tid":724556,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T23:59:26.000Z","msg":"推"}]}